    <item>
      <title>创纪录的现金需求引发人们猜测英国央行将结束债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/record-repo-demand-spurs-speculation-boe-will-end-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，银行对英格兰银行创纪录的现金需求可能会导致政策制定者在几个月内通过债券市场缓解金融状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/record-repo-demand-spurs-speculation-boe-will-end-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着前景的好转，世界经济有望摆脱滞胀困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/world-economy-looks-to-dodge-stagflation-rut-as-outlook-perks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织称，随着经济增长更具韧性且许多国家的通胀预计将以比此前预期更快的速度降温，世界经济前景正在好转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/world-economy-looks-to-dodge-stagflation-rut-as-outlook-perks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织将英国列为明年七国集团增长联盟的垫底</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/oecd-puts-britain-at-bottom-of-g-7-growth-league-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济合作与发展组织的最新预测显示，由于隐形税收和高利率挤压经济，明年英国的增长速度将比任何其他主要发达经济体都要慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/oecd-puts-britain-at-bottom-of-g-7-growth-league-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典破产数量连续 21 个月激增，没有任何缓解的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/swedish-bankruptcies-in-21-month-surge-show-no-signs-of-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Creditsafe 的数据显示，4 月份瑞典破产数量连续逐年增加，达到 21 个月。该公司预计，即使通胀放缓且降息临近，也不会立即出现缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/swedish-bankruptcies-in-21-month-surge-show-no-signs-of-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 06:57:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于利润超出预期，壳牌保持回购步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/shell-maintains-pace-of-buybacks-as-profit-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于第一季度利润降幅低于预期，壳牌公司保持了股票回购的步伐，继续关注股东回报，这已成为石油巨头的标志。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/shell-maintains-pace-of-buybacks-as-profit-beats-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 06:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>住友商事将在新的中期计划中提高股东回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/sumitomo-aims-to-bolster-shareholder-returns-in-new-midterm-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本住友商事株式会社表示，将回购股票并采取渐进式股息政策，使其与其他四大同行保持一致，以提高股东回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/sumitomo-aims-to-bolster-shareholder-returns-in-new-midterm-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:57:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国库存增加，油价跌至七周低点后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国原油库存大幅增加，加剧了对需求疲软的担忧，周三油价暴跌后收复了部分跌幅。]]></description>
